  hindiTitle `सामाजिक सुरक्षा संहिता, 2020`
  actYear (2020)
  ministry `Ministry of Labour and Employment`
  department undefined
  longTitle `An Act to amend and consolidate the laws relating to social security with the goal to extend social security to all employees and workers either in the organised or unorganised or any other sectors and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
